---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use | PricingNest" description="Terms of use, calculator limitations, and acceptable use for PricingNest.">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p>
      PricingNest provides informational calculators and editorial guides for pricing, packaging, and unit economics. The
      output is designed to help you think through decisions, not to replace legal, financial, tax, or procurement
      review.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="grid">
    <section class="card col8">
      <h2>Informational use only</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Calculator results are estimates based on the assumptions you enter. They may not reflect your actual contract
        terms, vendor pricing, customer mix, margin targets, or internal policy. You are responsible for checking whether
        an output is suitable before using it in a live pricing decision.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">No warranty</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        We provide the site and its content "as is" and "as available." While we try to keep formulas, examples, and
        explanations accurate, we do not guarantee that every page is complete, current, or free of error.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">User responsibility</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        You are responsible for validating your own inputs, checking outputs against source data, and deciding whether a
        recommendation fits your contracts, operations, and legal requirements. If a page looks unclear or outdated,
        treat it as a starting point and review it before relying on it.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">Acceptable use</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Do not use the site to submit harmful, abusive, or unlawful content.</li>
        <li>Do not attempt to disrupt the calculators, content delivery, or ad and consent systems.</li>
        <li>Do not copy or redistribute substantial site content without permission where copyright applies.</li>
        <li>Use the site in a way that respects other users and the integrity of the published models.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">Intellectual property</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        The site design, copy, structure, and tool logic are part of the PricingNest property unless otherwise noted. Third
        party names, trademarks, and referenced products remain the property of their respective owners.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">Corrections and contact</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        If you find an error, use the <a href="/contact/">Contact</a> page to send a correction request. We review
        meaningful correction notes before updating pages that affect retained tools or trust-critical explanations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <aside class="card col4">
      <h2>Summary</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Estimates only, not advice.</li>
        <li>Validate every input before use.</li>
        <li>Report issues through Contact.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">Related pages</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li><a href="/about/">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact/">Contact</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy policy</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cookie-policy/">Cookie policy</a></li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
